  "title": "Central Kitchen Helper ( SALARY FROM $2180 /11AM-8PM / SUN OFF ）",
  "description": "<p>· Cutting vegetable, meat, poultry, fish and mince meat</p><p>· Prepare sauces, spices, seasonings and marinades based on standard recipes</p><p>· Preparation and production of soup (Bak Kut Teh, Tonkatsu Soup etc.)</p><p>· Prepare gyoza ingredient, making gyoza & gyoza skin (by machine)</p><p>· Preparation and production of mochi</p><p>· Receive and store food products at designated area</p><p>· Packing of food and storage</p><p>· Baking of tarts</p><p>· Cleaning of equipment and tools and waste disposal</p><p>· Handle any other duties assigned by Manager</p><p>· Assist in back up noodle, bakery and packing department if needed</p><p>· Follow company safety SOP and wear safety equipment while working in the kitchen<br />Able to carry load up to 20kg.</p>",
